&lt;p&gt;Join us on our journey and help us create our new unannounced IP. We are seeking a Level Designer who is passionate about creating engaging and challenging combat experiences and locations players will love to explore. The ideal candidate should be curious, invested, and excited about experimenting with innovative ideas to create both the big and little moments in the game world that enhance the narrative and make it come to life.&lt;/p&gt;
